quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  26,137,Wannan abu bai zamõ ba fãce hãlãyen* mutãnen farko
  26,138,Kuma mũ ba mu zama waɗanda ake yi wa azãba ba
  26,139,"Sabõda haka suka ƙaryata shi, sai Muka halakar da sũ. Lalle ne a cikin wannan akwai ãyã, kuma mafi yawansu ba su kasance mãsu ĩmãni ba"
  26,140,"Kuma lalle ne, Ubangijinka, haƙĩƙa, Shi ne Mabuwãyi, Mai jin ƙai"
  26,141,Samũdãwa sun ƙaryata Manzanni
  26,142,"A lõkacin da ɗan'uwansu Sãlihu ya ce: \"Shin, bã zã ku bi Allah da taƙawa ba"
  26,143,"Lalle ne nĩ zuwã gare ku, Manzo ne, amintacce"
  26,144,"Sabõda haka ku bi Allah da taƙawa, kuma ku yi mini ɗã'ã"
  26,145,Kuma bã ni tambayar ku wata ijãra a kansa. Ijãrãta ba ta zama ba fãce da a Ubangijin halittu
  26,146,"Shin, anã barin ku* a cikin abin da yake a nan, kunã amintattu"
  26,147,A cikin gõnaki da marẽmari
  26,148,"Da shuke-shuke da dabĩ nai, 'ya'yan itãcensu hirtsi* mãsu narkẽwa a ciki"
  26,149,"Kuma kunã sassaƙa gidãje daga duwãtsu, kunã mãsu alfãhari"
  26,150,"Sabõda haka ku bi Allah da taƙawa, kuma ku yi mini ɗã'ã"
  26,151,Kada ku yi ɗã'ã ga umurnin maɓarnata
  26,152,"Waɗanda suke yin ɓarna a cikin ƙasa, kuma bã su kyautatãwa"
  26,153,"Suka ce: \"Kai daga mãsu sihiri kurum kake"
  26,154,"Bã kõwa kake ba, fãce mutum kamarmu. To, kã zo da wata ãyã idan kã kasance daga mãsu gaskiya"
  26,155,"Ya ce: \"Wannan rãkuma ce tanã da shan* yini, kuma kunã da shan yini sasanne"
  26,156,Kada ku shãfe ta da cũta har azãbar yini mai girmã ta shãfe ku
  26,157,Sai suka sõke ta sa'an nan suka wãyi gari sunã mãsu nadãma
  26,158,"Sabõda haka azãba ta kãma su. Lalle ne a cikin wannan akwai ãyã, kuma mafi yawansu, ba su kasance mãsu ĩmãni ba"
  26,159,"Lalle ne Ubangijinka, haƙĩ ƙa, Shĩ ne Mabuwayi, Mai jin ƙai"